We offer FREE SHIPPING, 1-3 business day Priority Mail within the Domestic US (including APOs). Shipments occur Monday - Saturday within 24 hours of payment received from a confirmed Paypal address. Purchases made on a weekend or holiday will ship out on the next business day.

Purchases will receive a tracking number to monitor your shipment. Please allow 24 to 48 hours for tracking information to update on the shipping company's website. This is normal; please do not be concerned if this is the case with your package.

Returns 
We do not accept returns. Please make sure you purchase the correct size. Not responsible for Nike imperfections.
